article_title: Anthem's Enrollment Soars Thanks To Obamacare's Medicaid Expansion

article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen

og.description: Anthem (ANTM) said its enrollment in government business is on a roll with double-digit percentage growth in the expanded Medicaid program for poor Americans under the Affordable Care Act. Anthem, releasing its second-quarter earnings that were ahead of Wall Street’s expectations, said its Medicaid membership was up 940,000, or nearly 20%, [...]
